headline: Canadian entrepreneurs gain competitive edge from AI adoption, GoDaddy research finds
summary: Artificial Intelligence (AI) is becoming more widespread amongst Canadian entrepreneurs, enhancing productivity and increasing sales, according to GoDaddy research.
